{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897713565,"sessionID":"ses_2843f9435ffeZ3zCsY9nzwDCy7","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc095ee001Qt4RqnbvdupY3K","messageID":"msg_d7bc08d1e001WTiCfeDOh75HX2","sessionID":"ses_2843f9435ffeZ3zCsY9nzwDCy7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-0bac38be98084611b00ccec426a7cfea","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-039 вҖ” Go еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ• (router/store/picod)\n2: \n3: ## жҰӮиҝ°\n4: \n5: жң¬ж–ҮжЎЈжҸҸиҝ°дәҶдёә agentcube йЎ№зӣ®дёӯ `pkg/router`гҖҒ`pkg/store` е’Ң `pkg/picod` жЁЎеқ—зј–еҶҷе…ЁйқўеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•зҡ„жҠҖжңҜе®һзҺ°и®ҫи®ЎгҖӮиҝҷдәӣжЁЎеқ—жһ„жҲҗдәҶзі»з»ҹзҡ„ж ёеҝғз»„д»¶пјҢиҙҹиҙЈи·Ҝз”ұгҖҒеӯҳеӮЁе’Ңд»Јз Ғжү§иЎҢеҠҹиғҪгҖӮ\n6: \n7: ## зӣ®ж Ү\n8: \n9: 1. дёә routerгҖҒstoreгҖҒpicod жЁЎеқ—жҸҗдҫӣе…Ёйқўзҡ„еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•иҰҶзӣ–\n10: 2. зЎ®дҝқд»Јз ҒиҙЁйҮҸе’ҢеҸҜйқ жҖ§\n11: 3. жҸҗдҫӣеҸҜз»ҙжҠӨзҡ„жөӢиҜ•еҹәзЎҖи®ҫж–Ҫ\n12: 4. йҒөеҫӘ Go жөӢиҜ•жңҖдҪіе®һи·ө\n13: \n14: ## жһ¶жһ„\n15: \n16: ### ж•ҙдҪ“жһ¶жһ„\n17: \n18: ```\n19: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n20: в”Ӯ                          router                                 в”Ӯ\n21: в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ         в”Ӯ\n22: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ   handlers   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  middleware  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  session_mgr в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ\n23: в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ         в”Ӯ\n24: в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ         в”Ӯ\n25: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ   jwt_mgr    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯresource_cacheв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ informer_mgr в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ\n26: в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ         в”Ӯ\n27: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n28:                               в”Ӯ\n29:                               в–ј\n30: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n31: в”Ӯ                           store                                 в”Ӯ\n32: в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ         в”Ӯ\n33: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ store_redis  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯstore_valkey  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    codec     в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ\n34: в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ         в”Ӯ\n35: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n36:                               в”Ӯ\n37:                               в–ј\n38: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n39: в”Ӯ                          picod                                  в”Ӯ\n40: в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ         в”Ӯ\n41: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ   handlers   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  middleware  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  auth_mgr    в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ\n42: в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ         в”Ӯ\n43: в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ         в”Ӯ\n44: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ workspace_mgrв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ status_rptr  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯinformr_mgr   в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ\n45: в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ         в”Ӯ\n46: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### жЁЎеқ—иҒҢиҙЈ\n50: \n51: #### Router жЁЎеқ—\n52: - **handlers.go**: HTTP иҜ·жұӮеӨ„зҗҶйҖ»иҫ‘\n53: - **middleware.go**: дёӯй—ҙд»¶пјҲи®ӨиҜҒгҖҒйҷҗжөҒгҖҒж—Ҙеҝ—гҖҒзӣ‘жҺ§пјү\n54: - **session_manager.go**: дјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶе’ҢжІҷзӣ’з”ҹе‘Ҫе‘Ёжңҹ\n55: - **jwt.go**: JWT д»ӨзүҢз”ҹжҲҗе’ҢйӘҢиҜҒ\n56: - **resource_cache.go**: Kubernetes иө„жәҗзј“еӯҳ\n57: - **informer_manager.go**: Kubernetes informer з®ЎзҗҶ\n58: - **server.go**: HTTP жңҚеҠЎеҷЁеҗҜеҠЁе’Ңй…ҚзҪ®\n59: \n60: #### Store жЁЎеқ—\n61: - **store.go**: еӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү\n62: - **store_redis.go**: Redis еӯҳеӮЁе®һзҺ°\n63: - **store_valkey.go**: ValKey еӯҳеӮЁе®һзҺ°\n64: - **codec.go**: ж•°жҚ®еәҸеҲ—еҢ–/еҸҚеәҸеҲ—еҢ–\n65: - **singleton.go**: еӯҳеӮЁе®һдҫӢз®ЎзҗҶ\n66: \n67: #### Picod жЁЎеқ—\n68: - **handlers.go**: ж–Үд»¶ж“ҚдҪңе’Ңе‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢеӨ„зҗҶ\n69: - **middleware.go**: и®ӨиҜҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶\n70: - **auth.go**: и®ӨиҜҒз®ЎзҗҶеҷЁ\n71: - **workspace_manager.go**: е·ҘдҪңз©әй—ҙз®ЎзҗҶ\n72: - **status_reporter.go**: зҠ¶жҖҒжҠҘе‘Ҡ\n73: - **informer.go**: Kubernetes informer йӣҶжҲҗ\n74: - **server.go**: HTTP жңҚеҠЎеҷЁ\n75: \n76: ## ж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„\n77: \n78: ### Router жЁЎеқ—ж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„\n79: \n80: #### ж ёеҝғзұ»еһӢ\n81: \n82: ```go\n83: // Server дё»жңҚеҠЎеҷЁз»“жһ„\n84: type Server struct {\n85:     config         *Config\n86:     engine         *gin.Engine\n87:     httpServer     *http.Server\n88:     sessionManager SessionManager\n89:     storeClient    store.Store\n90:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n91:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n92:     handler        *Handler\n93:     limiter        *ConcurrencyLimiter\n94:     metrics        *Metrics\n95:     mu             sync.RWMutex\n96: }\n97: \n98: // Handler HTTP еӨ„зҗҶеҷЁ\n99: type Handler struct {\n100:     sessionManager SessionManager\n101:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n102:     reverseProxy   *ReverseProxy\n103: }\n104: \n105: // SessionManager дјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶеҷЁжҺҘеҸЈ\n106: type SessionManager interface {\n107:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n108:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n109:     ListSessions(ctx context.Context) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n110:     InitializeInformers(clientset kubernetes.Interface, namespace string, resyncPeriod time.Duration) error\n111:     StartInformers()\n112:     StopInformers()\n113:     WaitForCacheSync(ctx context.Context) bool\n114: }\n115: \n116: // ResourceCache иө„жәҗзј“еӯҳ\n117: type ResourceCache struct {\n118:     mu               sync.RWMutex\n119:     agentRuntimes    map[string]*agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime\n120:     codeInterpreters map[string]*agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\n121:     resourceVersions map[string]string\n122: }\n123: ```\n124: \n125: #### й”ҷиҜҜзұ»еһӢ\n126: \n127: ```go\n128: // HTTPError HTTP й”ҷиҜҜжҺҘеҸЈ\n129: type HTTPError interface {\n130:     Error() string\n131:     HTTPStatusCode() int\n132:     ErrorCode() string\n133: }\n134: \n135: // SandboxNotFoundError жІҷзӣ’жңӘжүҫеҲ°й”ҷиҜҜ\n136: type SandboxNotFoundError struct {\n137:     SessionID string\n138:     Name      string\n139:     Namespace string\n140:     Kind      string\n141: }\n142: \n143: // ValidationError йӘҢиҜҒй”ҷиҜҜ\n144: type ValidationError struct {\n145:     Field   string\n146:     Message string\n147: }\n148: \n149: // WorkloadManagerError е·ҘдҪңиҙҹиҪҪз®ЎзҗҶеҷЁй”ҷиҜҜ\n150: type WorkloadManagerError struct {\n151:     Message string\n152:     Code    int\n153: }\n154: ```\n155: \n156: ### Store жЁЎеқ—ж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„\n157: \n158: ```go\n159: // Store еӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈ\n160: type Store interface {\n161:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n162:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n163:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n164:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n165:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n166:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n167:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n168:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n169:     Close() error\n170: }\n171: \n172: // redisStore Redis еӯҳеӮЁе®һзҺ°\n173: type redisStore struct {\n174:     cli                  *redis.Client\n175:     sessionPrefix        string\n176:     expiryIndexKey       string\n177:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n178: }\n179: ```\n180: \n181: ### Picod жЁЎеқ—ж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„\n182: \n183: ```go\n184: // Server PicoD жңҚеҠЎеҷЁ\n185: type Server struct {\n186:     engine           *gin.Engine\n187:     config           Config\n188:     authManager      *AuthManager\n189:     startTime        time.Time\n190:     workspaceDir     string\n191:     httpServer       *http.Server\n192:     k8sClient        *K8sClient\n193:     workspaceManager *WorkspaceManager\n194:     statusReporter   *StatusReporter\n195:     informerManager  *InformerManager\n196: }\n197: \n198: // ExecuteRequest жү§иЎҢиҜ·жұӮ\n199: type ExecuteRequest struct {\n200:     Command     []string            `json:\"command\"`\n201:     WorkingDir  string              `json:\"workingDir\"`\n202:     Env         map[string]string   `json:\"env\"`\n203:     Timeout     string              `json:\"timeout\"`\n204: }\n205: \n206: // ExecuteResponse жү§иЎҢе“Қеә”\n207: type ExecuteResponse struct {\n208:     Stdout    string      `json:\"stdout\"`\n209:     Stderr    string      `json:\"stderr\"`\n210:     ExitCode  int         `json:\"exitCode\"`\n211:     Duration  float64     `json:\"duration\"`\n212:     StartTime time.Time   `json:\"startTime\"`\n213:     EndTime   time.Time   `json:\"endTime\"`\n214: }\n215: ```\n216: \n217: ## API еҘ‘зәҰ\n218: \n219: ### Router жЁЎеқ— API\n220: \n221: #### HTTP з«ҜзӮ№\n222: \n223: ```\n224: # еҒҘеә·жЈҖжҹҘ\n225: GET /health/live\n226: GET /health/ready\n227: \n228: # дјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶ\n229: POST /v1/sessions/namespaces/:namespace/:kind/:name\n230: GET  /v1/sessions/:sessionID\n231: \n232: # иө„жәҗи°ғз”Ё\n233: ANY /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path\n234: ANY /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path\n235: ```\n236: \n237: #### еҶ…йғЁжҺҘеҸЈ\n238: \n239: ```go\n240: // SessionManager жҺҘеҸЈж–№жі•зӯҫеҗҚ\n241: GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n242: CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n243: ListSessions(ctx context.Context) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n244: \n245: // JWTManager жҺҘеҸЈж–№жі•зӯҫеҗҚ\n246: GenerateToken(sessionID string) (string, error)\n247: ValidateToken(token string) (*JWTClaims, error)\n248: ```\n249: \n250: ### Store жЁЎеқ— API\n251: \n252: ```go\n253: // Store жҺҘеҸЈж–№жі•зӯҫеҗҚ\n254: Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n255: GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n256: StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n257: UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n258: DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n259: ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n260: ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n261: UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n262: Close() error\n263: ```\n264: \n265: ### Picod жЁЎеқ— API\n266: \n267: #### HTTP з«ҜзӮ№\n268: \n269: ```\n270: # еҒҘеә·жЈҖжҹҘ\n271: GET /health\n272: \n273: # и®ӨиҜҒдҝқжҠӨзҡ„з«ҜзӮ№\n274: POST /api/execute\n275: POST /api/files\n276: GET  /api/files\n277: GET  /api/files/*path\n278: ```\n279: \n280: #### иҜ·жұӮ/е“Қеә”зұ»еһӢ\n281: \n282: ```go\n283: // ExecuteRequest е‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢиҜ·жұӮ\n284: type ExecuteRequest struct {\n285:     Command     []string          `json:\"command\"`\n286:     WorkingDir  string            `json:\"workingDir\"`\n287:     Env         map[string]string `json:\"env\"`\n288:     Timeout     string            `json:\"timeout\"`\n289: }\n290: \n291: // ExecuteResponse е‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢе“Қеә”\n292: type ExecuteResponse struct {\n293:     Stdout    string    `json:\"stdout\"`\n294:     Stderr    string    `json:\"stderr\"`\n295:     ExitCode  int       `json:\"exitCode\"`\n296:     Duration  float64   `json:\"duration\"`\n297:     StartTime time.Time `json:\"startTime\"`\n298:     EndTime   time.Time `json:\"endTime\"`\n299: }\n300: \n301: // FileEntry ж–Үд»¶жқЎзӣ®\n302: type FileEntry struct {\n303:     Name     string      `json:\"name\"`\n304:     Size     int64       `json:\"size\"`\n305:     Modified time.Time   `json:\"modified\"`\n306:     Mode     string      `json:\"mode\"`\n307:     IsDir    bool        `json:\"isDir\"`\n308: }\n309: ```\n310: \n311: ## й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n312: \n313: ### й”ҷиҜҜеұӮж¬Ўз»“жһ„\n314: \n315: ```\n316: HTTPError (interface)\n317: в”ңв”Җв”Җ SandboxNotFoundError\n318: в”ңв”Җв”Җ SessionExpiredError\n319: в”ңв”Җв”Җ WorkloadManagerError\n320: в””в”Җв”Җ ValidationError\n321: ```\n322: \n323: ### й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶзӯ–з•Ҙ\n324: \n325: #### Router жЁЎеқ—й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n326: \n327: 1. **йӘҢиҜҒй”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ 400 зҠ¶жҖҒз Ғе’ҢиҜҰз»Ҷй”ҷиҜҜдҝЎжҒҜ\n328: 2. **жңӘжүҫеҲ°й”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ 404 зҠ¶жҖҒз Ғ\n329: 3. **и®ӨиҜҒй”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ 401 зҠ¶жҖҒз Ғ\n330: 4. **жңҚеҠЎеҷЁй”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ 500 зҠ¶жҖҒз Ғе№¶и®°еҪ•ж—Ҙеҝ—\n331: \n332: #### Store жЁЎеқ—й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n333: \n334: 1. **иҝһжҺҘй”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ wrapped й”ҷиҜҜпјҢеҢ…еҗ«еҺҹе§Ӣй”ҷиҜҜ\n335: 2. **жңӘжүҫеҲ°й”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ `ErrNotFound`\n336: 3. **еәҸеҲ—еҢ–й”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ wrapped й”ҷиҜҜ\n337: 4. **йӘҢиҜҒй”ҷиҜҜ**: еҸӮж•°ж ЎйӘҢеӨұиҙҘж—¶иҝ”еӣһжҸҸиҝ°жҖ§й”ҷиҜҜ\n338: \n339: #### Picod жЁЎеқ—й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n340: \n341: 1. **е‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢй”ҷиҜҜ**: жҚ•иҺ·е№¶иҝ”еӣһйҖҖеҮәз Ғ\n342: 2. **ж–Үд»¶ж“ҚдҪңй”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһйҖӮеҪ“зҡ„ HTTP зҠ¶жҖҒз Ғ\n343: 3. **и®ӨиҜҒй”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһ 401 зҠ¶жҖҒз Ғ\n344: 4. **и¶…ж—¶й”ҷиҜҜ**: иҝ”еӣһзү№ж®Ҡзҡ„и¶…ж—¶йҖҖеҮәз Ғ\n345: \n346: ### й”ҷиҜҜз Ғе®ҡд№ү\n347: \n348: ```go\n349: // Router й”ҷиҜҜз Ғ\n350: const (\n351:     ErrSandboxNotFound        = \"SANDBOX_NOT_FOUND\"\n352:     ErrSessionExpired         = \"SESSION_EXPIRED\"\n353:     ErrWorkloadManagerError   = \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_ERROR\"\n354:     ErrValidationError        = \"VALIDATION_ERROR\"\n355:     ErrJWTSigningFailed       = \"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"\n356:     ErrSandboxUnreachable     = \"SANDBOX_UNREACHABLE\"\n357:     ErrServerOverloaded       = \"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"\n358:     ErrSessionManagerNotReady = \"SESSION_MANAGER_NOT_READY\"\n359: )\n360: \n361: // Store й”ҷиҜҜз Ғ\n362: var ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"store: not found\")\n363: \n364: // Picod й”ҷиҜҜз Ғ\n365: const (\n366:     ErrInvalidCommand    = \"INVALID_COMMAND\"\n367:     ErrEmptyCommand      = \"EMPTY_COMMAND\"\n368:     ErrInvalidTimeout    = \"INVALID_TIMEOUT\"\n369:     ErrMissingAuthHeader = \"MISSING_AUTH_HEADER\"\n370:     ErrFileNotFound      = \"FILE_NOT_FOUND\"\n371:     ErrDirectoryNotFound = \"DIRECTORY_NOT_FOUND\"\n372:     ErrPathIsDirectory   = \"PATH_IS_DIRECTORY\"\n373:     ErrServerInternal    = \"SERVER_INTERNAL\"\n374: )\n375: ```\n376: \n377: ## жөӢиҜ•зӯ–з•Ҙ\n378: \n379: ### жөӢиҜ•з»„з»Үз»“жһ„\n380: \n381: ```\n382: pkg/\n383: в”ңв”Җв”Җ router/\n384: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ handlers_test.go\n385: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ middleware_test.go\n386: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ session_manager_test.go\n387: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ jwt_test.go\n388: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ resource_cache_test.go\n389: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ informer_manager_test.go\n390: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ config_test.go\n391: в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ server_test.go\n392: в”ңв”Җв”Җ store/\n393: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ store_test.go\n394: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ store_redis_test.go\n395: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ store_valkey_test.go\n396: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ codec_test.go\n397: в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ singleton_test.go\n398: в””в”Җв”Җ picod/\n399:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ handlers_test.go\n400:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ middleware_test.go\n401:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ auth_test.go\n402:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace_manager_test.go\n403:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ status_reporter_test.go\n404:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ informer_test.go\n405:     в””в”Җв”Җ server_test.go\n406: ```\n407: \n408: ### жөӢиҜ•жЎҶжһ¶е’Ңе·Ҙе…·\n409: \n410: #### дё»иҰҒжөӢиҜ•жЎҶжһ¶\n411: - **ж ҮеҮҶеә“ `testing`**: Go ж ҮеҮҶжөӢиҜ•жЎҶжһ¶\n412: - **testify/assert**: ж–ӯиЁҖеә“пјҢжҸҗдҫӣжӣҙдё°еҜҢзҡ„ж–ӯиЁҖж–№жі•\n413: - **testify/require**: еҝ…иҰҒж–ӯиЁҖпјҢеӨұиҙҘж—¶з«ӢеҚіеҒңжӯўжөӢиҜ•\n414: \n415: #### Mock е’Ң Stub е·Ҙе…·\n416: - **httptest**: HTTP жөӢиҜ•жңҚеҠЎеҷЁ\n417: - **fake kubernetes clientset**: Kubernetes е®ўжҲ·з«ҜжЁЎжӢҹ\n418: - **miniredis**: Redis еҶ…еӯҳж•°жҚ®еә“жЁЎжӢҹ\n419: - **иҮӘе®ҡд№ү fake е®һзҺ°**: з”ЁдәҺиҮӘе®ҡд№үжҺҘеҸЈзҡ„жЁЎжӢҹ\n420: \n421: #### иҫ…еҠ©е·Ҙе…·\n422: - **gonic/gin.TestMode**: Gin жЎҶжһ¶жөӢиҜ•жЁЎејҸ\n423: - **google/uuid**: UUID з”ҹжҲҗе’ҢйӘҢиҜҒ\n424: - **testify/mock**: Mock жҺҘеҸЈе®һзҺ°\n425: \n426: ### жөӢиҜ•иҰҶзӣ–зҺҮзӣ®ж Ү\n427: \n428: | жЁЎеқ—     | зӣ®ж ҮиҰҶзӣ–зҺҮ | дјҳе…Ҳзә§ |\n429: |---------|-----------|--------|\n430: | router  | вүҘ80%      | й«ҳ     |\n431: | store   | вүҘ85%      | й«ҳ     |\n432: | picod   | вүҘ75%      | дёӯ     |\n433: \n434: ### жөӢиҜ•еҲҶзұ»\n435: \n436: #### еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•\n437: \n438: **зӣ®ж Ү**: жөӢиҜ•еҚ•дёӘеҮҪж•°жҲ–ж–№жі•зҡ„иЎҢдёә\n439: \n440: **зү№зӮ№**:\n441: - еҝ«йҖҹжү§иЎҢпјҲжҜ«з§’зә§пјү\n442: - ж— еӨ–йғЁдҫқиө–\n443: - еҸҜйҮҚеӨҚиҝҗиЎҢ\n444: - иҰҶзӣ–жүҖжңүд»Јз Ғи·Ҝеҫ„\n445: \n446: **зӨәдҫӢ**:\n447: ```go\n448: func TestNewHandler(t *testing.T) {\n449:     jwtManager, err := NewJWTManager(fake.NewSimpleClientset(), \"test\")\n450:     require.NoError(t, err)\n451: \n452:     handler := NewHandler(nil, jwtManager, nil)\n453:     assert.NotNil(t, handler)\n454:     assert.NotNil(t, handler.jwtManager)\n455: }\n456: ```\n457: \n458: #### йӣҶжҲҗжөӢиҜ•\n459: \n460: **зӣ®ж Ү**: жөӢиҜ•еӨҡдёӘз»„д»¶д№Ӣй—ҙзҡ„дәӨдә’\n461: \n462: **зү№зӮ№**:\n463: - дҪҝз”Ёзңҹе®һдҫқиө–зҡ„жЁЎжӢҹзүҲжң¬\n464: - жөӢиҜ•з»„д»¶й—ҙзҡ„ж•°жҚ®жөҒ\n465: - йӘҢиҜҒжҺҘеҸЈеҘ‘зәҰ\n466: \n467: **зӨәдҫӢ**:\n468: ```go\n469: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession(t *testing.T) {\n470:     server := httptest.NewServer(http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n471:         // Mock workload manager response\n472:     }))\n473:     defer server.Close()\n474: \n475:     fakeStore := &fakeStore{}\n476:     manager, err := NewSessionManager(fakeStore, server.URL)\n477:     require.NoError(t, err)\n478: \n479:     sessionID, sandboxInfo, err := manager.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n480:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n481:     assert.NotEmpty(t, sessionID)\n482:     assert.NotNil(t, sandboxInfo)\n483: }\n484: ```\n485: \n486: #### иЎЁй©ұеҠЁжөӢиҜ•\n487: \n488: **зӣ®ж Ү**: жөӢиҜ•еҮҪж•°еңЁдёҚеҗҢиҫ“е…ҘдёӢзҡ„иЎҢдёә\n489: \n490: **зү№зӮ№**:\n491: - жё…жҷ°зҡ„жөӢиҜ•з”ЁдҫӢз»„з»Ү\n492: - жҳ“дәҺж·»еҠ ж–°зҡ„жөӢиҜ•еңәжҷҜ\n493: - дёҖиҮҙзҡ„ж–ӯиЁҖйҖ»иҫ‘\n494: \n495: **зӨәдҫӢ**:\n496: ```go\n497: func TestHandleHealthReady(t *testing.T) {\n498:     tests := []struct {\n499:         name           string\n500:         sessionManager SessionManager\n501:         jwtManager     *JWTManager\n502:         expectedStatus int\n503:     }{\n504:         {\n505:             name:           \"session manager not ready\",\n506:             sessionManager: nil,\n507:             jwtManager:     func() *JWTManager { mgr, _ := NewJWTManager(fake.NewSimpleClientset(), \"test\"); return mgr }(),\n508:             expectedStatus: http.StatusServiceUnavailable,\n509:         },\n510:         {\n511:             name:           \"JWT manager not ready\",\n512:             sessionManager: nil,\n513:             jwtManager:     nil,\n514:             expectedStatus: http.StatusServiceUnavailable,\n515:         },\n516:     }\n517: \n518:     for _, tt := range tests {\n519:         t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n520:             handler := NewHandler(tt.sessionManager, tt.jwtManager, nil)\n521:             // ... test implementation\n522:         })\n523:     }\n524: }\n525: ```\n526: \n527: ### Mock зӯ–з•Ҙ\n528: \n529: #### жҺҘеҸЈ Mock\n530: \n531: ```go\n532: // Fake Store е®һзҺ°\n533: type fakeStore struct {\n534:     sandboxes map[string]*types.SandboxInfo\n535: }\n536: \n537: func (fs *fakeStore) GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error) {\n538:     if fs.sandboxes == nil {\n539:         return nil, store.ErrNotFound\n540:     }\n541:     sandbox, exists := fs.sandboxes[sessionID]\n542:     if !exists {\n543:         return nil, store.ErrNotFound\n544:     }\n545:     return sandbox, nil\n546: }\n547: ```\n548: \n549: #### HTTP Mock\n550: \n551: ```go\n552: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession(t *testing.T) {\n553:     server := httptest.NewServer(http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n554:         if r.Method == http.MethodPost && r.URL.Path == \"/v1/agent-runtime\" {\n555:             w.Header().Set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n556:             w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n557:             w.Write([]byte(`{\n558:                 \"sessionId\": \"test-session-id\",\n559:                 \"sandboxId\": \"test-sandbox-id\",\n560:                 \"sandboxName\": \"test-sandbox\",\n561:                 \"entryPoints\": []\n562:             }`))\n563:         }\n564:     }))\n565:     defer server.Close()\n566: \n567:     // ... test implementation\n568: }\n569: ```\n570: \n571: ### жөӢиҜ•иҫ…еҠ©еҮҪж•°\n572: \n573: #### и®ҫзҪ®е’Ңжё…зҗҶ\n574: \n575: ```go\n576: func setupTestServer(t *testing.T) *Server {\n577:     workspace := t.TempDir()\n578:     _, publicKey := generateTestKeyPair(t)\n579:     publicKeyPEM := publicKeyToPEM(t, publicKey)\n580: \n581:     os.Setenv(PublicKeyEnvVar, publicKeyPEM)\n582:     defer os.Unsetenv(PublicKeyEnvVar)\n583: \n584:     config := Config{\n585:         Port:      0,\n586:         Workspace: workspace,\n587:     }\n588: \n589:     server, err := NewServer(config)\n590:     require.NoError(t, err)\n591:     gin.SetMode(gin.TestMode)\n592: \n593:     return server\n594: }\n595: ```\n596: \n597: #### ж•°жҚ®з”ҹжҲҗ\n598: \n599: ```go\n600: func generateTestSandboxInfo() *types.SandboxInfo {\n601:     return &types.SandboxInfo{\n602:         SessionID:    \"test-session-\" + uuid.New().String(),\n603:         SandboxName:  \"test-sandbox\",\n604:         WorkloadName: \"test-workload\",\n605:         Namespace:    \"default\",\n606:         Kind:         \"AgentRuntime\",\n607:         Status:       \"running\",\n608:         CreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n609:         ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour),\n610:         PodIP:        \"10.0.0.1\",\n611:     }\n612: }\n613: ```\n614: \n615: ### жөӢиҜ•еңәжҷҜ\n616: \n617: #### Router жЁЎеқ—жөӢиҜ•еңәжҷҜ\n618: \n619: **handlers_test.go**\n620: - вң“ Handler еҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n621: - вң“ еҒҘеә·жЈҖжҹҘз«ҜзӮ№ (live/ready)\n622: - вң“ дјҡиҜқ ID жҸҗеҸ–\n623: - вң“ дјҡиҜқеҲӣе»әйӘҢиҜҒ\n624: - вң“ иө„жәҗи°ғз”ЁйӘҢиҜҒ\n625: - вң“ й”ҷиҜҜе“Қеә”ж јејҸ\n626: \n627: **middleware_test.go**\n628: - вң“ е№¶еҸ‘йҷҗеҲ¶дёӯй—ҙд»¶\n629: - вң“ ж—Ҙеҝ—дёӯй—ҙд»¶\n630: - вң“ жҒўеӨҚдёӯй—ҙд»¶\n631: - вң“ е…іиҒ” ID дёӯй—ҙд»¶\n632: - вң“ JWT и®ӨиҜҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶\n633: - вң“ жҢҮж Үдёӯй—ҙд»¶\n634: \n635: **session_manager_test.go**\n636: - вң“ дјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶеҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n637: - вң“ Informer еҲқе§ӢеҢ–е’ҢеҗҜеҠЁ\n638: - вң“ дјҡиҜқеҲӣе»әпјҲжҲҗеҠҹ/еӨұиҙҘпјү\n639: - вң“ жІҷзӣ’иҺ·еҸ–пјҲзј“еӯҳе‘Ҫдёӯ/жңӘе‘Ҫдёӯпјү\n640: - вң“ дјҡиҜқеҲ—иЎЁ\n641: - вң“ иө„жәҗзҠ¶жҖҒжЈҖжҹҘ\n642: - вң“ иө„жәҗеҲ йҷӨжЈҖжөӢ\n643: \n644: **jwt_test.go**\n645: - вң“ JWT д»ӨзүҢз”ҹжҲҗ\n646: - вң“ JWT д»ӨзүҢйӘҢиҜҒ\n647: - вң“ иҝҮжңҹд»ӨзүҢеӨ„зҗҶ\n648: - вң“ ж— ж•Ҳд»ӨзүҢеӨ„зҗҶ\n649: \n650: **resource_cache_test.go**\n651: - вң“ иө„жәҗзј“еӯҳжӣҙж–°\n652: - вң“ иө„жәҗзј“еӯҳжҹҘиҜў\n653: - вң“ иө„жәҗзј“еӯҳеҲ йҷӨ\n654: - вң“ иө„жәҗзүҲжң¬жЈҖжҹҘ\n655: - вң“ е№¶еҸ‘е®үе…ЁжҖ§\n656: \n657: **informer_manager_test.go**\n658: - вң“ Informer з®ЎзҗҶеҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n659: - вң“ Informer еҗҜеҠЁе’ҢеҒңжӯў\n660: - вң“ зј“еӯҳеҗҢжӯҘзӯүеҫ…\n661: - вң“ з©әе®ўжҲ·з«ҜйӣҶеӨ„зҗҶ\n662: \n663: **config_test.go**\n664: - вң“ й…ҚзҪ®йӘҢиҜҒ\n665: - вң“ й»ҳи®Өй…ҚзҪ®\n666: - вң“ TLS й…ҚзҪ®\n667: - вң“ и¶…ж—¶й…ҚзҪ®\n668: \n669: **server_test.go**\n670: - вң“ жңҚеҠЎеҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n671: - вң“ жңҚеҠЎеҷЁеҗҜеҠЁе’Ңе…ій—ӯ\n672: - вң“ дёӯй—ҙд»¶еә”з”Ё\n673: - вң“ и·Ҝз”ұи®ҫзҪ®\n674: - вң“ жҢҮж Үж”¶йӣҶ\n675: \n676: #### Store жЁЎеқ—жөӢиҜ•еңәжҷҜ\n677: \n678: **store_test.go**\n679: - вң“ еӯҳеӮЁиҝһжҺҘжөӢиҜ•\n680: - вң“ жІҷзӣ’еӯҳеӮЁе’ҢиҺ·еҸ–\n681: - вң“ жІҷзӣ’жӣҙж–°\n682: - вң“ жІҷзӣ’еҲ йҷӨ\n683: - вң“ дјҡиҜқжҙ»еҠЁжӣҙж–°\n684: - вң“ иҝҮжңҹжІҷзӣ’еҲ—иЎЁ\n685: - вң“ йқһжҙ»и·ғжІҷзӣ’еҲ—иЎЁ\n686: - вң“ й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n687: \n688: **store_redis_test.go**\n689: - вң“ Redis иҝһжҺҘ\n690: - вң“ Redis зү№е®ҡж“ҚдҪң\n691: - вң“ з®ЎйҒ“ж“ҚдҪң\n692: - вң“ зҙўеј•з®ЎзҗҶ\n693: \n694: **store_valkey_test.go**\n695: - вң“ ValKey иҝһжҺҘ\n696: - вң“ ValKey зү№е®ҡж“ҚдҪң\n697: - вң“ дёҺ Redis е®һзҺ°е…је®№жҖ§\n698: \n699: **codec_test.go**\n700: - вң“ жІҷзӣ’дҝЎжҒҜеәҸеҲ—еҢ–\n701: - вң“ жІҷзӣ’дҝЎжҒҜеҸҚеәҸеҲ—еҢ–\n702: - вң“ й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n703: \n704: **singleton_test.go**\n705: - вң“ еҚ•дҫӢжЁЎејҸ\n706: - вң“ дёҚеҗҢеӯҳеӮЁзұ»еһӢеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n707: - вң“ й…ҚзҪ®йӘҢиҜҒ\n708: \n709: #### Picod жЁЎеқ—жөӢиҜ•еңәжҷҜ\n710: \n711: **handlers_test.go**\n712: - вң“ е‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢеӨ„зҗҶеҷЁ\n713: - вң“ ж–Үд»¶дёҠдј еӨ„зҗҶеҷЁпјҲmultipartпјү\n714: - вң“ ж–Үд»¶дёҠдј еӨ„зҗҶеҷЁпјҲbase64пјү\n715: - вң“ ж–Үд»¶еҲ—иЎЁеӨ„зҗҶеҷЁ\n716: - вң“ ж–Үд»¶дёӢиҪҪеӨ„зҗҶеҷЁ\n717: - вң“ еҒҘеә·жЈҖжҹҘеӨ„зҗҶеҷЁ\n718: - вң“ и·Ҝеҫ„жё…зҗҶ\n719: - вң“ ж–Үд»¶жЁЎејҸи§Јжһҗ\n720: \n721: **middleware_test.go**\n722: - вң“ и®ӨиҜҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶\n723: - вң“ жңүж•Ҳд»ӨзүҢеӨ„зҗҶ\n724: - вң“ ж— ж•Ҳд»ӨзүҢеӨ„зҗҶ\n725: - вң“ зјәеӨұи®ӨиҜҒеӨҙеӨ„зҗҶ\n726: \n727: **auth_test.go**\n728: - вң“ и®ӨиҜҒз®ЎзҗҶеҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n729: - вң“ д»ӨзүҢз”ҹжҲҗе’ҢйӘҢиҜҒ\n730: - вң“ еҜҶй’ҘеҜ№з”ҹжҲҗ\n731: - вң“ й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶ\n732: \n733: **workspace_manager_test.go**\n734: - вң“ е·ҘдҪңз©әй—ҙеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n735: - вң“ ж–Үд»¶ж“ҚдҪң\n736: - вң“ зӣ®еҪ•з®ЎзҗҶ\n737: - вң“ жқғйҷҗеӨ„зҗҶ\n738: \n739: **status_reporter_test.go**\n740: - вң“ зҠ¶жҖҒжҠҘе‘ҠеҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n741: - вң“ зҠ¶жҖҒжӣҙж–°\n742: - вң“ е‘ЁжңҹжҖ§жҠҘе‘Ҡ\n743: \n744: **informer_test.go**\n745: - вң“ Informer и®ҫзҪ®\n746: - вң“ дәӢд»¶еӨ„зҗҶ\n747: - вң“ зј“еӯҳеҗҢжӯҘ\n748: \n749: **server_test.go**\n750: - вң“ жңҚеҠЎеҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–\n751: - вң“ жңҚеҠЎеҷЁеҗҜеҠЁе’Ңе…ій—ӯ\n752: - вң“ и·Ҝз”ұжіЁеҶҢ\n753: - вң“ дёӯй—ҙд»¶еә”з”Ё\n754: \n755: ### жөӢиҜ•жү§иЎҢ\n756: \n757: #### жң¬ең°жөӢиҜ•иҝҗиЎҢ\n758: \n759: ```bash\n760: # иҝҗиЎҢжүҖжңүжөӢиҜ•\n761: go test ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/... ./pkg/picod/...\n762: \n763: # иҝҗиЎҢзү№е®ҡеҢ…жөӢиҜ•\n764: go test ./pkg/router/\n765: \n766: # иҝҗиЎҢзү№е®ҡжөӢиҜ•\n767: go test ./pkg/router/ -run TestNewHandler\n768: \n769: # иҝҗиЎҢжөӢиҜ•е№¶жҳҫзӨәиҰҶзӣ–зҺҮ\n770: go test -cover ./pkg/router/...\n771: \n772: # з”ҹжҲҗиҰҶзӣ–зҺҮжҠҘе‘Ҡ\n773: go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/...\n774: go tool cover -html=coverage.out\n775: \n776: # иҝҗиЎҢеҹәеҮҶжөӢиҜ•\n777: go test -bench=. ./pkg/...\n778: \n779: # иҝҗиЎҢз«һжҖҒжЈҖжөӢ\n780: go test -race ./pkg/...\n781: ```\n782: \n783: #### CI/CD йӣҶжҲҗ\n784: \n785: ```yaml\n786: # .github/workflows/test.yml зӨәдҫӢ\n787: name: Tests\n788: \n789: on: [push, pull_request]\n790: \n791: jobs:\n792:   test:\n793:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n794:     steps:\n795:       - uses: actions/checkout@v3\n796:       - uses: actions/setup-go@v4\n797:         with:\n798:           go-version: '1.21'\n799:       - name: Run tests\n800:         run: |\n801:           go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out -covermode=atomic ./pkg/...\n802:       - name: Upload coverage\n803:         uses: codecov/codecov-action@v3\n804:         with:\n805:           files: ./coverage.out\n806: ```\n807: \n808: ### жөӢиҜ•жңҖдҪіе®һи·ө\n809: \n810: 1. **жөӢиҜ•е‘ҪеҗҚ**: дҪҝз”ЁжҸҸиҝ°жҖ§зҡ„жөӢиҜ•еҗҚз§°пјҢж јејҸдёә `Test<FunctionName>_<Scenario>`\n811: \n812: 2. **иЎЁй©ұеҠЁжөӢиҜ•**: еҜ№дәҺжңүеӨҡдёӘжөӢиҜ•еңәжҷҜзҡ„еҮҪж•°пјҢдҪҝз”ЁиЎЁй©ұеҠЁжөӢиҜ•\n813: \n814: 3. **еӯҗжөӢиҜ•**: дҪҝз”Ё `t.Run()` з»„з»Үзӣёе…іжөӢиҜ•\n815: \n816: 4. **ж–ӯиЁҖ**: дҪҝз”Ё `assert` иҝӣиЎҢдёҖиҲ¬ж–ӯиЁҖпјҢ`require` иҝӣиЎҢе…ій”®ж–ӯиЁҖ\n817: \n818: 5. **жё…зҗҶ**: дҪҝз”Ё `defer` жҲ– `t.Cleanup()` иҝӣиЎҢиө„жәҗжё…зҗҶ\n819: \n820: 6. **йҡ”зҰ»**: жҜҸдёӘжөӢиҜ•еә”иҜҘжҳҜзӢ¬з«Ӣзҡ„пјҢдёҚдҫқиө–дәҺе…¶д»–жөӢиҜ•\n821: \n822: 7. **е№¶еҸ‘е®үе…Ё**: жөӢиҜ•е№¶еҸ‘д»Јз Ғж—¶дҪҝз”Ё `-race` ж Үеҝ—\n823: \n824: 8. **Mock дҫқиө–**: дҪҝз”Ё fake е®һзҺ°жӣҝд»Јзңҹе®һдҫқиө–\n825: \n826: 9. **й”ҷиҜҜжөӢиҜ•**: жөӢиҜ•й”ҷиҜҜи·Ҝеҫ„пјҢдёҚд»…д»…жҳҜжҲҗеҠҹи·Ҝеҫ„\n827: \n828: 10. **иҫ№з•ҢжқЎд»¶**: жөӢиҜ•иҫ№з•ҢжқЎд»¶е’Ңзү№ж®Ҡжғ…еҶө\n829: \n830: ## е®һж–Ҫи®ЎеҲ’\n831: \n832: ### йҳ¶ж®ө 1: Router жЁЎеқ—жөӢиҜ•пјҲдјҳе…Ҳзә§пјҡй«ҳпјү\n833: \n834: 1. е®Ңе–„ `handlers_test.go`\n835: 2. е®Ңе–„ `middleware_test.go`\n836: 3. е®Ңе–„ `session_manager_test.go`\n837: 4. е®Ңе–„ `jwt_test.go`\n838: 5. ж–°еўһ `resource_cache_test.go`\n839: 6. ж–°еўһ `informer_manager_test.go`\n840: 7. е®Ңе–„ `config_test.go`\n841: 8. ж–°еўһ `server_test.go`\n842: \n843: ### йҳ¶ж®ө 2: Store жЁЎеқ—жөӢиҜ•пјҲдјҳе…Ҳзә§пјҡй«ҳпјү\n844: \n845: 1. е®Ңе–„ `store_test.go`\n846: 2. ж–°еўһ `store_redis_test.go`\n847: 3. ж–°еўһ `store_valkey_test.go`\n848: 4. ж–°еўһ `codec_test.go`\n849: 5. ж–°еўһ `singleton_test.go`\n850: \n851: ### йҳ¶ж®ө 3: Picod жЁЎеқ—жөӢиҜ•пјҲдјҳе…Ҳзә§пјҡдёӯпјү\n852: \n853: 1. е®Ңе–„ `handlers_test.go`\n854: 2. е®Ңе–„ `middleware_test.go`\n855: 3. е®Ңе–„ `auth_test.go`\n856: 4. ж–°еўһ `workspace_manager_test.go`\n857: 5. ж–°еўһ `status_reporter_test.go`\n858: 6. ж–°еўһ `informer_test.go`\n859: 7. е®Ңе–„ `server_test.go`\n860: \n861: ### йӘҢж”¶ж ҮеҮҶ\n862: \n863: - жүҖжңүж–°жөӢиҜ•йҖҡиҝҮ\n864: - д»Јз ҒиҰҶзӣ–зҺҮиҫҫж Ү\n865: - ж— з«һжҖҒжқЎд»¶иӯҰе‘Ҡ\n866: - жөӢиҜ•жү§иЎҢж—¶й—ҙеҗҲзҗҶ\n867: - CI/CD жөҒж°ҙзәҝйӣҶжҲҗжҲҗеҠҹ\n868: \n869: ## дҫқиө–е…ізі»\n870: \n871: ### жөӢиҜ•дҫқиө–\n872: \n873: ```go\n874: // go.mod дёӯзҡ„жөӢиҜ•дҫқиө–\n875: require (\n876:     github.com/stretchr/testify v1.8.4  // жөӢиҜ•жЎҶжһ¶\n877:     github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.32.0  // Redis жЁЎжӢҹ\n878:     k8s.io/client-go v0.28.0  // Kubernetes е®ўжҲ·з«ҜпјҲеҢ…еҗ« fake е®һзҺ°пјү\n879: )\n880: ```\n881: \n882: ### иҝҗиЎҢж—¶дҫқиө–\n883: \n884: ```go\n885: // дё»иҰҒиҝҗиЎҢж—¶дҫқиө–\n886: require (\n887:     github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.9.1  // Web жЎҶжһ¶\n888:     github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.0.0  // JWT еӨ„зҗҶ\n889:     github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.0.5  // Redis е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n890:     k8s.io/api v0.28.0  // Kubernetes API\n891:     k8s.io/apimachinery v0.28.0  // Kubernetes API machinery\n892:     k8s.io/client-go v0.28.0  // Kubernetes е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n893: )\n894: ```\n895: \n896: ## жҖ§иғҪиҖғиҷ‘\n897: \n898: ### жөӢиҜ•жҖ§иғҪдјҳеҢ–\n899: \n900: 1. **е№¶иЎҢжөӢиҜ•**: дҪҝз”Ё `t.Parallel()` иҝҗиЎҢзӢ¬з«ӢжөӢиҜ•\n901: 2. **зј“еӯҳйҮҚз”Ё**: еңЁеҢ…зә§еҲ«еҲқе§ӢеҢ–е…ұдә«иө„жәҗ\n902: 3. **йҖүжӢ©жҖ§иҝҗиЎҢ**: дҪҝз”Ё `-run` ж Үеҝ—иҝҗиЎҢзү№е®ҡжөӢиҜ•\n903: 4. **и¶…ж—¶жҺ§еҲ¶**: дёәй•ҝж—¶й—ҙиҝҗиЎҢзҡ„жөӢиҜ•и®ҫзҪ®и¶…ж—¶\n904: \n905: ### еҹәеҮҶжөӢиҜ•\n906: \n907: ```go\n908: func BenchmarkResourceCache_GetAgentRuntime(b *testing.B) {\n909:     cache := NewResourceCache()\n910:     ar := &agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n911:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n912:             Name:      \"test\",\n913:             Namespace: \"default\",\n914:         },\n915:     }\n916:     cache.UpdateAgentRuntime(ar)\n917: \n918:     b.ResetTimer()\n919:     for i := 0; i < b.N; i++ {\n920:         cache.GetAgentRuntime(\"default\", \"test\")\n921:     }\n922: }\n923: ```\n924: \n925: ## ж–ҮжЎЈ\n926: \n927: ### жөӢиҜ•ж–ҮжЎЈ\n928: \n929: жҜҸдёӘжөӢиҜ•ж–Үд»¶еә”еҢ…еҗ«пјҡ\n930: - еҢ…зә§еҲ«зҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈжіЁйҮҠ\n931: - еӨҚжқӮжөӢиҜ•еҮҪж•°зҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈжіЁйҮҠ\n932: - жөӢиҜ•иҫ…еҠ©еҮҪж•°зҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈжіЁйҮҠ\n933: \n934: ### зӨәдҫӢ\n935: \n936: ```go\n937: // Package router_test provides unit tests for the router package.\n938: //\n939: // These tests cover the HTTP handlers, middleware, session management,\n940: // JWT authentication, resource caching, and informer management.\n941: package router_test\n942: \n943: // TestNewHandler verifies that a new Handler instance is created correctly.\n944: // It ensures that the handler is properly initialized with the provided\n945: // JWT manager and that the handler is not nil.\n946: func TestNewHandler(t *testing.T) {\n947:     // ... implementation\n948: }\n949: ```\n950: \n951: ## з»ҙжҠӨе’Ңжӣҙж–°\n952: \n953: ### жөӢиҜ•з»ҙжҠӨжҢҮеҚ—\n954: \n955: 1. **д»Јз ҒеҸҳжӣҙж—¶жӣҙж–°жөӢиҜ•**: дҝ®ж”№д»Јз Ғж—¶еҗҢжӯҘжӣҙж–°зӣёе…іжөӢиҜ•\n956: 2. **е®ҡжңҹе®ЎжҹҘиҰҶзӣ–зҺҮ**: е®ҡжңҹжЈҖжҹҘжөӢиҜ•иҰҶзӣ–зҺҮжҠҘе‘Ҡ\n957: 3. **йҮҚжһ„жөӢиҜ•**: йҡҸзқҖд»Јз Ғжј”иҝӣйҮҚжһ„жөӢиҜ•д»ҘжҸҗй«ҳеҸҜз»ҙжҠӨжҖ§\n958: 4. **еҲ йҷӨиҝҮж—¶жөӢиҜ•**: з§»йҷӨдёҚеҶҚзӣёе…ізҡ„жөӢиҜ•з”ЁдҫӢ\n959: 5. **ж·»еҠ ж–°жөӢиҜ•**: дёәж–°еҠҹиғҪж·»еҠ зӣёеә”зҡ„жөӢиҜ•\n960: \n961: ### жҢҒз»ӯж”№иҝӣ\n962: \n963: 1. **зӣ‘жҺ§жөӢиҜ•жү§иЎҢж—¶й—ҙ**: иҜҶеҲ«е№¶дјҳеҢ–ж…ўйҖҹжөӢиҜ•\n964: 2. **еҲҶжһҗеӨұиҙҘжөӢиҜ•**: е»әз«ӢжөӢиҜ•еӨұиҙҘеҲҶжһҗжөҒзЁӢ\n965: 3. **еҲҶдә«жөӢиҜ•жңҖдҪіе®һи·ө**: еңЁеӣўйҳҹдёӯжҺЁе№ҝжөӢиҜ•жңҖдҪіе®һи·ө\n966: 4. **иҮӘеҠЁеҢ–жөӢиҜ•жӣҙж–°**: е°ҪеҸҜиғҪиҮӘеҠЁеҢ–жөӢиҜ•з»ҙжҠӨд»»еҠЎ\n967: \n968: ## жҖ»з»“\n969: \n970: жң¬и®ҫи®Ўж–ҮжЎЈдёә AR-039 Go еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•жҸҗдҫӣдәҶе…Ёйқўзҡ„жҠҖжңҜе®һж–ҪжҢҮеҚ—гҖӮйҖҡиҝҮйҒөеҫӘжң¬ж–ҮжЎЈдёӯжҸҸиҝ°зҡ„жһ¶жһ„гҖҒж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„гҖҒAPI еҘ‘зәҰгҖҒй”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶе’ҢжөӢиҜ•зӯ–з•ҘпјҢеҸҜд»Ҙдёә routerгҖҒstore е’Ң picod жЁЎеқ—жһ„е»әй«ҳиҙЁйҮҸгҖҒеҸҜз»ҙжҠӨзҡ„еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•еҘ—д»¶гҖӮ\n971: \n972: е®һж–ҪжӯӨи®ҫи®Ўе°ҶеёҰжқҘд»ҘдёӢеҘҪеӨ„пјҡ\n973: - жҸҗй«ҳд»Јз ҒиҙЁйҮҸе’ҢеҸҜйқ жҖ§\n974: - еҠ йҖҹејҖеҸ‘е’Ңи°ғиҜ•иҝҮзЁӢ\n975: - йҷҚдҪҺеӣһеҪ’йЈҺйҷ©\n976: - жҸҗдҫӣд»Јз ҒиЎҢдёәзҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈ\n977: - ж”ҜжҢҒе®үе…Ёзҡ„йҮҚжһ„е’Ңжј”иҝӣ\n978: \n979: йҖҡиҝҮйҳ¶ж®өеҢ–зҡ„е®һж–Ҫи®ЎеҲ’е’ҢжҳҺзЎ®зҡ„йӘҢж”¶ж ҮеҮҶпјҢеҸҜд»ҘзЎ®дҝқжөӢиҜ•е·ҘдҪңзҡ„жңүеәҸиҝӣиЎҢе’ҢжҲҗеҠҹдәӨд»ҳгҖӮ\n\n(End of file - total 979 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-039 вҖ” Go еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ• (router/store/picod)\n\n## жҰӮиҝ°\n\nжң¬ж–ҮжЎЈжҸҸиҝ°дәҶдёә agentcube йЎ№зӣ®дёӯ `pkg/router`гҖҒ`pkg/store` е’Ң `pkg/picod` жЁЎеқ—зј–еҶҷе…ЁйқўеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•зҡ„жҠҖжңҜе®һзҺ°и®ҫи®ЎгҖӮиҝҷдәӣжЁЎеқ—жһ„жҲҗдәҶзі»з»ҹзҡ„ж ёеҝғз»„д»¶пјҢиҙҹиҙЈи·Ҝз”ұгҖҒеӯҳеӮЁе’Ңд»Јз Ғжү§иЎҢеҠҹиғҪгҖӮ\n\n## зӣ®ж Ү\n\n1. дёә routerгҖҒstoreгҖҒpicod жЁЎеқ—жҸҗдҫӣе…Ёйқўзҡ„еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•иҰҶзӣ–\n2. зЎ®дҝқд»Јз ҒиҙЁйҮҸе’ҢеҸҜйқ жҖ§\n3. жҸҗдҫӣеҸҜз»ҙжҠӨзҡ„жөӢиҜ•еҹәзЎҖи®ҫж–Ҫ\n4. йҒөеҫӘ Go жөӢиҜ•жңҖдҪіе®һи·ө\n\n## жһ¶жһ„\n\n### ж•ҙдҪ“жһ¶жһ„\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                          router                                 в”Ӯ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"